docs.title: SATPLAN
docs.text:
Welcome to the SATPLAN documentation! This documentation provides an overview of the SATPLAN library, its features, and how to use it to benchmark and implement satellite task planning algorithms.

Warning

This documentation (and project) is a work in progress. If you have any questions or suggestions, please feel free to open an issue on the GitHub repository

docs.title: Library API
docs.text: This section provides detailed information about all the classes, functions, and modules available in the SATPLAN library. Each entry includes a brief description, parameters, return values, and examples where applicable.

docs.title: Tutorials
docs.text: This section provides step-by-step guides and examples to help you get started with the SATPLAN library.
